{"tid":1610951,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"文宣組再次出動，警狗殺人要填命！！","createTime":"2019-10-01T23:52:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-02T04:50:22.000Z","uid":2820,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"43780186065305bcc491a170405f9b75791087a7","tid":1610951,"uid":2820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T23:52:12.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: maroon;\">警察已經出真槍殺人。仲可以唔出聲到幾時？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n示威您可以話自己有包袱唔出得去，理解既。<br />\n但幫手宣傳文宣得啦掛？<br />\n大家幫幫手推香港狗察暴行上世界既頭條！！！</span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">一齊#chest4hk !!!</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港警察對鎗械/武力使用上喺香港係一言堂，所以對胸射擊呢件事點都要好似#eye4hk咁上到國際先俾到哪怕丁點壓力政府考慮向警隊開刀同埋最最重要俾多啲低成本高曝光參與機會外國同路人。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">幫手打國際線reddit 又好Twitter 又好ig都好 將#chest4hk呢個hashtag blast出去</span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">文宣：</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oW1LqhO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoW1LqhO.jpg&h=a65d5236&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TsRLqhP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTsRLqhP.jpg&h=cb239173&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n順帶一提，今日12點半中環見！黑西裝癱瘓全中環！<br />\n今日罷到工就罷，罷到請出中環。<br />\n罷唔到請lunch time 出， 謝謝。<br />\n活動傳送門： <a href=\"https://lih.kg/1610862\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1610862</a>"},{"pid":"0a3ff9f6f386bc37688ca182a3464516eab9e409","tid":1610951,"uid":2820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T23:54:29.000Z","msg":"推 #chest4hk"},{"pid":"69fffaaa343b55c5d3793251ea06843f01f9ccb3","tid":1610951,"uid":2820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T23:56:26.000Z","msg":"推 #chest4hk"},{"pid":"d824becf853cdd37310ae4e7cbc8024091ed96c2","tid":1610951,"uid":160842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T23:56:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zqeEuOA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzqeEuOA.jpg&h=e91696cb&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YZ91H8A.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYZ91H8A.jpg&h=72e1aef6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"716d90a34c0fc448e158b7bd3c5f81ff99c70b2e","tid":1610951,"uid":227981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0a3ff9f6f386bc37688ca182a3464516eab9e409","tid":1610951,"uid":2820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T23:54:29.000Z","msg":"推 #chest4hk"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T23:57:42.000Z","msg":"而家香港係一個誰大誰惡誰正確既時代<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1610696\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1610696</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"d26ded06c6ef52cde904e07e54598aaa8a1a9321","tid":1610951,"uid":2820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d824becf853cdd37310ae4e7cbc8024091ed96c2","tid":1610951,"uid":160842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T23:56:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zqeEuOA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzqeEuOA.jpg&h=e91696cb&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"htt